\begin_layout Frame
\begin_inset Argument 4
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Model Setup
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Frame
A small open economy with AR(1) potential output stream 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ y_{t}\right\} _{t=0}^{\infty}$
\end_inset

:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\ln(y_{t+1})=\rho\ln(y_{t})+\varepsilon_{t+1},\quad\text{where }\varepsilon_{t+1}\sim N(0,\sigma_{\varepsilon}^{2})
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Frame
Identical households rank stochastic consumption streams according to:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\mathbb{E}_{0}\left[\sum_{t=0}^{\infty}\beta^{t}u\left(c_{t}\right)\right]
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Frame
The government try to smooth consumption by borrowing from (and lending to) foreign creditors.
\end_layout

